<li>Builds speaking confidence quickly</li>
<li>Natural pronunciation development</li>
<li>No need to look at a screen</li>
<li>Well-structured curriculum</li>
<li>Audio quality is excellent</li>
<li>Good for auditory learners</li>
<li>No translation dependency</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-3">❌ Cons</h3>
<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
<li>Expensive for audio-only content</li>
<li>No visual learning elements</li>
<li>30-minute lessons may be too long</li>
<li>Limited vocabulary beyond lessons</li>
<li>No grammar explanations</li>
<li>Cannot pause/resume within lessons</li>
<li>Requires consistent time commitment</li>
<li>Not ideal for visual learners</li>
</ul>
</div>
